                                         throws java.io.IOException
        Creates a new EdHD assignment
        Parameters:
        props - - A full assignment definition with a primary (assignment) and secondary (validation) configuration
        primarySrc - - a zip file containing the necessary source files for the primary configuration. If no source files are needed for the primary configuration, this should be null
        secondarySrc - - a zip file containing the necessary source files for the secondary configuration. If no source files are needed for the secondary configuration, this should be null
        Returns:
        UUID of the newly created assignment or null if it could not be created

        Updates and existing EdHD assignment
        Parameters:
        props - - A full assignment definition with a primary (assignment) and secondary (validation) configuration
        primarySrc - - a zip file containing the necessary source files for the primary configuration. If the configuration contains a primarySrcLoc, the existing file will be reused
        secondarySrc - - a zip file containing the necessary source files for the secondary configuration. If the configuration contains a srcLoc, the existing file will be reused
        Returns:
        UUID of the updated assignment or null if it could not be updated
